CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper October 1, 1960, pg. 18, reads: "Winners - There were plenty of victory smiles at the Centre Avenue YMCA last Friday night during the first All-Star amateur boxing show of the season... The other photo shows Chuck Raston, also of the Daniels A. C., after he defeated Ray Casey of Lee Moore A. C. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Men surrounding and raising fists of boxer Chuck Raston after victorious match against Ray Casey at All-Star amateur boxing show, Centre Avenue YMCA
